  $escape$nmap — Phishing Simulation Scans with Script Arguments$escape$,
  $escape$Use nmap's -script-args flag to inject custom inputs for phishing simulation scans. For instance, you can use the http-headers script to simulate a phishing email with embedded malicious links. Set the 'http-user-agent' argument to a specific user agent string for more realistic simulations.$escape$,
